{"tid":600191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭捐3萬元　胡志偉指續監察政府：看不到大和解","createTime":"2018-03-21T05:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T06:35:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d753378473d20b3819516db43a43d959280f7117","tid":600191,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180321/s00001/c69b1d25f0d76d8b62aabb611f879014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180321%2Fs00001%2Fc69b1d25f0d76d8b62aabb611f879014.jpg&h=3863dd1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥昨晚出席民主黨黨慶晚宴，應捐3萬元，並在社交網站上載相片，標註「大和解」。民主黨主席胡志偉今日強調，該黨會繼續監察和批判政府，不會因3萬元改變看法，又指政府不只要與一個政黨和解，而是要與整個社會和解，他現時看不到政府實現了「大和解」。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉認為，社會對政府不信任，故政府更應讓社會多參與政策過程，例如在高鐵一地兩檢多聆聽意見，在《國歌法》本地立法則應以白紙草案形式諮詢公眾。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，不擔心民主黨收林鄭月娥捐款會引起市民反彈，因該黨會繼續指出政府的不當施政，又指若捐款是無條件，看不到理由要拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180321/s00001/1521610907504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180321%2Fs00001%2F1521610907504&d=LDSP%2F%2Ft5rpHQa9iNo9Y1w4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=917cdddd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180321%2Fs00001%2F1521610907504&h=475aed70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180321/s00001/1521610907504</a>"},{"pid":"2af001ba30d2c4a90d88d6357dc197820f1bc50d","tid":600191,"uid":131259,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"777咁騎劫法都幾核突"},{"pid":"5b093a97d613359edf4c401fc1ca51a1c401d6eb","tid":600191,"uid":156659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"三萬蚊就可以撚狗你地民主黨<br />\n真係抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97be704068f2ba6cfa1d38f7b18d8ca6b4bd1cf","tid":600191,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"收檔啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6666b7f73b67d9b2552e1033728cf4097ec9ed","tid":600191,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"反間計，水洗都唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64f247e0cd29f866e38c497c11c87f9d570c824","tid":600191,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2af001ba30d2c4a90d88d6357dc197820f1bc50d","tid":600191,"uid":131259,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"777咁騎劫法都幾核突"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"民主黨不知幾開心"},{"pid":"f19ffc00243e5ec35eeec12e9cc7d782c9f485b3","tid":600191,"uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"收共產黨錢都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f495e2448fb98c6525292e3f08c916bdaffc5d3c","tid":600191,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e49cbc164fb97b6eb039d9fab3272f80a4c5f8b","tid":600191,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"3萬蚊毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n民主黨0政治敏感度"},{"pid":"6167912604182b0f326449b6226dc664699fec96","tid":600191,"uid":7318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"一啲政治智慧都冇"},{"pid":"3c06afb3483617a002ab2ef864e0a5eaf1ba9d1c","tid":600191,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:07:42.000Z","msg":"